ActEmergency Management Act
SubjectProvincial Emergency Financial Assistance Order No. 218, Alberta
PrecisPROVINCIAL EMERGENCY FINANCIAL ASSISTANCE ORDER NO. 218 which makes a declaration of federal concern and authorizes the Minister to provide financial assistance to ALBERTA with respect to the spring flooding that occurred from April 10 to 30, 2018.
